{"tid":2273053,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【防山寨之戰】池底撈、渠底撈、下海底撈？海底撈1日申請177商標防山寨版品牌","createTime":"2020-11-05T12:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T06:39:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd333dd79d07daf79e7bcfd3e164fd5761fd40d","tid":2273053,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2795000/2795276/Haidilao_Hot_Pot_in_OP_Mall_202005_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2795000%2F2795276%2FHaidilao_Hot_Pot_in_OP_Mall_202005_600.jpg&h=038ec4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國火鍋店「海底撈」擁有高知名度，有商家就利用類似的名字作招徠，最後被「海底撈」控告。為了防止山寨品牌再現，「海底撈」最近開始大量申請商標，當中包括池底撈、渠底撈、海底撿等商標。<br />\n<br />\n避免捲入官司「海底撈」1日申請177個商標<br />\n<br />\n「海底撈」早前控告「河底撈」，指其採用的藝術字樣，「河」字的三點水呈現河流狀、「底」字下面的點呈現魚形狀，而整個招牌上方還有一條跳躍的魚，與他們的商標高度相似，因而控告「河底撈」商標侵權。但長沙市天心區法院審理後認為，兩者商標雖然都有「底撈」二字，但整體字形有所差異，讀音也不一樣，加上「海底撈」公司旗下所有店鋪全是川菜系列的火鍋，而「河底撈」餐廳則是典型的湘菜系列，法院最終認定「河底撈」不構成對原告「海底撈」公司的註冊商標權侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為了避免上述情況發生，海底撈近日大量申請商標。據「天眼查」網頁顯示，海底撈在 10 月 28 日，短短 1 日共申請 177 個商標，如「上海底撈」、「黑海撈」、「海底嘮」、「池底撈」、「渠底撈」、「清底撈」、「海底撿」等，把一般人能想到的商標都註冊，據悉上述商標都正在申請中。<br />\n<br />\n多個內地企業搶先註冊山寨商標<br />\n<br />\n近年內地大企業為了防範山寨版公司，紛紛擔先註冊山寨商標。例如電子商務公司阿里巴巴已註冊「阿里媽媽」、「阿里爺爺」、「阿里奶奶」、「阿里哥哥」等商標。此外，中國電話品牌小米也將「藍米」、「黑米」、「紫米」、「橙米」等商標全部註冊，而國有企業五糧液除了註冊「五狠液」，還註冊了「六糧液」、「三糧液」、「七糧液」、「八糧液」的商標。"},{"pid":"e932247b52cc87d68e30bb5bd68aae4020b51b61","tid":2273053,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:42:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/123512664973980/permalink/659754431349798/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F123512664973980%2Fpermalink%2F659754431349798%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8tAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=5b6bda01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/123512664973980/permalink/659754431349798/</a>"},{"pid":"de18140d554e1bb6a899481c6ffd3cd19cc752a0","tid":2273053,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"坑渠撈"},{"pid":"29c908e8ccc34819652332b759b0ccd9a92d4965","tid":2273053,"uid":254745,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:43:46.000Z","msg":"黑海撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇死海撈"},{"pid":"ad805822a3a88abe271b424ea30ff3615f20c1d1","tid":2273053,"uid":101616,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"渠底撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n符合國情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69eb7eeb86e426c147e6abbe04bba186e52fa7c","tid":2273053,"uid":46927,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"袋底撈應該未申請"},{"pid":"30e39adbced2539872051b0f2e8523a969f469c2","tid":2273053,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc4f94d4c95021cc8dbacbca8d3a870adf24ded","tid":2273053,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"不如申請埋「無得撈」啦<br />\n支国依家有幾億人用緊呢個朵啊 邊個申請定呢個商標註冊邊個都會發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8b62da1e2c34e7908097ecd9c6342c43bf1c90","tid":2273053,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a540804c03b1f7a0b34dd78f3687ab3660aeada5","tid"